Package kea.schedule.scheduleservice.services

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CRUDServiceInterface<E extends ModelInterface>
    Default CRUD interface for services.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionService
    Handles CRUD for actions and handles when actions are triggered, to alert any microservice listening for the specific action.
    AuthenticationService
    Handles user authentication.
    CourseService
    CRUD for Course
    GroupService
    CRUD for Group
    LectureItemService
    CRUD for LectureItem
    LectureService
    CRUD for Lecture
    LectureSubjectService
    CRUD for LectureSubject
    ModelService
    Factory for Model services
    MSSessionEntityService
    CRUD for MSSession
    ScheduleService
    The ScheduleService create schedules, by interpretating Course > Lecture > Lecture Subject and Lecture Item.
    ScheduleSettingService
    CRUD for ScheduleSetting A ScheduleSetting is a single name and value, and contains simple information to save in the database.
    SetupService
    The setup service, provides an easy way to setup the microservices.
    SubjectPriorityService
    CRUD for SubjectPriority
    UserService
    CRUD for User
